Subject: [PATCH 09/13] Add in-tree Mesh backend (--with-malloc-preload=mesh)

Vendor Plasma/Mesh as a C++ allocator shipped only as
libglibc_malloc_mesh.so for LD_PRELOAD (not linked into libc), with embed
stubs retained for registration experiments.
